document_data.mainbody: '''Stall Street''' was a small road located in the city of [[Zhentil Keep]] during the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Stall Street was located in Zhentil Keep's [[Zhentil Keep/Common Quarter|Common Quarter]] in the eastern section of the city. The road originated on the [[Street of Sorrow]], branching southwest for just a block before ending at the wall of the [[Zhentil Keep/Inner Quarter|Inner Quarter]].
